    neo:source "Source document: ZEN FLESH, ZEN BONES, Chapter: 8. Great Waves, paragraph number 4, sentence number 5 on page 21"^^xsd:string ;
    neo:text "Do this and you will be the greatest wrestler in the land.’"^^xsd:string .

